Package com.igormaznitsa.prol.libraries

The package contains prolog library related classes, the prol core library is placed in the package.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
PredicateProcessor The auxulary inside class describes a predicate processor.
PredicateTemplate The class describes a template for a predicate argument.
ProlAbstractLibrary The core class describes a prolog library contains predicates and operators.
ProlCoreLibrary The Prol Core Library This class extends a prol abstract library and contain a lot of useful definitions
ProlGraphicLibrary The class implements the Prol Graphic library and it can be used to show to draw simple graphic primitives and save images.
ProlGraphicLibrary.ImageToClipboard  
ProlLibraryWrapper This class allows to wrap classes which are non successors of the ProlAbstractLibrary which can be used as prol libraries To sign a method as a predicate you need just to place the WrappedPredicate annotation before it.
ProlStringLibrary The class implements the Prol String library allows to manipulate with strings
 

Package com.igormaznitsa.prol.libraries Description
